EngineRelatedEvent, FolderRelatedEvent, MonitorEvent, ResourceRelatedEvent, SiteRelatedEvent
public abstract class JSpiderEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventVisitable

Base class of all JSpider API events. All events that will be dispatched towards JSpider modules will extends directly or indirectly from this class. $Id: JSpiderEvent.java,v 1.5 2003/03/23 15:44:48 vanrogu Exp $

Author:
Günther Van Roey
